metadata.name: Birth
metadata.description:
Chuang Tzu once dreamt that he had become a butterfly. Upon awakening he wondered whether it was a human being who had just dreamt of being a butterfly, or a butterfly which had dreamt that it had become a human being. 

Can it be that my whole life is someone elseâ€™s dream?
